Understanding the challenges posed by the inherent ambiguity of textual prompts, I also developed a learnable style token that refines these prompts, enhancing the precision of style conveyance. My research not only demonstrates superior performance against existing benchmarks but also explores creative avenues such as style combination through mixed inversion noise. I am passionate about pushing the boundaries of generative models and contributing to the evolving landscape of AI-driven creativity.

